HEADWORD: Philanthropinism
<hw>Phil`an*throp"i*nism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A system
of education on so-called natural principles, attempted in Germany in
the last century by Basedow, of Dessau.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

